      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nLi - Could this patch be causing a memory leak? I see the following in the logs for mmp at https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/c2ee23a0-2a01-11e5-b04d-5254006e85c2:\n19:14:03:CMD: shadow-10vm6.shadow.whamcloud.com lsmod | grep lnet > /dev/null && lctl dl | grep ' ST '\n19:14:03:LustreError: 29022:0:(class_obd.c:633:cleanup_obdclass()) obd_memory max: 9675035, leaked: 1071656\n19:14:03:\n19:14:03:Memory leaks detected\n19:14:15:mmp returned 0\n\nThanks.",
